       correction:"1. y_r=+2sin(2pi(x/lambda + ft)) (inversion de phase)\n2. y_tot=4sin(2pi x/lambda) cos(2pi ft)\n3. Ventre: x=lambda/4 + n lambda/2 · Noeud: x=n lambda/2",
